NK039(ti)032:1: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)032:2: ma ma ru lu rak+sha re ma ti /
NK039(ti)032:3: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah snying po'o //
NK039(ti)032:4: ru ru tsa dur a shug me /
NK039(ti)032:5: pra ti ru dra kha shag rag+mo h'u /
NK039(ti)032:9: ru ru be ru ro h'u /
NK039(ti)032:10: ti sta tha ba to si la /
NK039(ti)032:11: rag+mo snying kha la rag+mo thun b+h+yo dza dzah rbad pa'o //
NK039(ti)032:12: ru lu re ma ti sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)032:14: pra ma rag+mo ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah
NK039(ti)032:15: kha rag de khem dza dzah kha le thun b+h+yo
NK039(ti)032:16: thun b+h+yo ma mo b+h+yoh bsad pa'o //
NK039(ti)032:17: h'u rag+mo ni sha ku ru rbad /
NK039(ti)032:18: rag ma at+ya dza dzah ti khem kha lem b+h+yoo /
NK039(ti)032:19: sa ma ya ch+gee mo r+n+ri ma ra ya h'u phatah lha mo'i rgyud kyi sngags ni 'adi'o //
NK039(ti)032:20: dpal ldan lha mo'i nag mo'i rgyud kyi srog snying la /
NK039(ti)032:21: ru ru ru ru bi tish+tha ba to si /
NK039(ti)032:22: ru ru ro ru bi tish+tha ba to pi tsi
NK039(ti)032:23: sa la a shug me h'u b+h+yo dzah khol mo
NK039(ti)032:24: re ma ti'i srog snying la /
NK039(ti)032:25: ru ru ru ru be ta h'u ti ti ba to si /
NK039(ti)032:27: ti kha rog+mo h'u b+h+yoh ma ma kha mun tra
NK039(ti)032:28: ba tra ba tra trag rag+sha tsit+ta kha rag ma
NK039(ti)032:29: / re ma ti sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)032:30: bra ma ma h+aa ti pra dun b+h+yo ru lu
NK039(ti)032:31: ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah de ni srog 'dren pa'i
NK039(ti)032:32: sngags yin te sa ya bzlas na ma mo mngon
NK039(ti)032:33: du 'ong / bye ba bzlas na phyag rgya ston par byed /
NK039(ti)032:34: 'bum phrag gis kyang dngos grub mtshan ma ster /
NK039(ti)032:35: khol mo'i snying po bzlas ma thag nas 'ong /
NK039(ti)032:36: sa ma ya du ling rag+sha si /
NK039(ti)032:41: ru lu ru lu ru lu ru lu /
